import React, { Component } from 'react'
import { CurrencyDiv, MenuItem, NavDiv, NavItems, SearchDiv, ThemeConverter } from './styles'
import { Link } from "react-router-dom";

export default class NavBar extends Component {
    render() {
        return (
            <NavDiv>
                <NavItems>
                    <MenuItem>
                        <Link to="/coins">Coins</Link>
                    </MenuItem>
                    <MenuItem>
                        <Link to="/portfolio">Portfolio</Link>
                    </MenuItem>
                    <SearchDiv>
                    </SearchDiv>
                    <CurrencyDiv>
                    </CurrencyDiv>
                    <ThemeConverter>
                    </ThemeConverter>
                </NavItems>
            </NavDiv>
        )
    }
}
